S.FORM: I 1945 a miheca saka 10 folad saka 13 a romi'ad masofoc ci Dési Bouterse, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Suriname anini i ci Dési Bouterse, patirengan a romi'ad i 2010 a miheca saka 8 folad saka 12 a romi'ad.
